目标。 2024年12月27日，小米股价创下2022年以来新高，盘中触及34.95港元/股。 雷军在公开演讲时曾表示，小米做大模型的思路和很多公司不太一样，选择主力突破的是轻量化和本地部署。对于小米这样无论在手机还是造车上都讲究“性价比”的公司而言，如何在烧钱的大模型业务中平衡成本，无疑是雷军考虑的核心问题。而这，或许也是拥有DeepSeek-V2研发背景的罗福莉被雷军看中的原因。 小米集团财报显示，今年第三季度，小米集团实现总收入925亿元，同比增长30.5%；实现经调整净利润63亿元，同比增长4.4%。第三季度，小米智能电动汽车等创新业务收入97亿元，毛利率环比提升1.7个百分点达17.1%，净亏损持续收窄至15亿元。 内容来源雷军亲自挖人！为95后“天才少女”开出千万年薪_罗福莉_小米_DeepSeek"},"attached_info":"CkEIpdOWmfaz0/tPEAMaCTExMjYyMzk4NCD9+se7BjAAOPoLQBFyCjgyMzg0NDEzMTl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"36 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-45f55c2e9b4a60e28dccd0b62530048d_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"18_1735622373.19679","card_id":"Q_568579345","target":{"id":568579345,"title":"为什么西班牙的火腿可以生吃？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/568579345","type":"question","created":1669268398,"answer_count":411,"follower_count":859,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[304,617,14007,52672,56908],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"现在据说国内有些高端的金华火腿也能生吃了？是什么原理啊？怎么可以生吃呢？包括号称的无菌鸡蛋，据说直接生吃也没有问题。而且不腥"},"attached_info":"Cj8IpdOWmfaz0/tPEAMaCDg4NjMzMzMzIK6H/JsGMAA42wZAEnIJNTY4NTc5MzQ1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"32 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-4ff57b71fdee72297428c470d647d438_r.jpg?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"19_1735622373.20081","card_id":"Q_7487972594","target":{"id":7487972594,"title":"作为家长，你们会潜移默化的教孩子人情世故吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/7487972594","type":"question","created":1734791164,"answer_count":57,"follower_count":167,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2146,4719,13095,2911519,3785